            <title>2.2.8</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 13:39:38 -0400</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/hoomanaskari/mac-dictate-anywhere</link>
            <sparkle:version>19</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.2.8</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Dictate Anywhere 2.2.8

- Added an English Compact (110M) Parakeet model option with a smaller download and lower memory use.
- Improved startup handling for accessibility permissions, hotkey monitoring, and engine preparation.
- Fixed app reopening so Dictate Anywhere comes back reliably from the Dock, menu, and settings flows.
- Improved OpenRouter model matching for dynamic variant IDs and clarified model capability messaging.
]]></description>
